Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:08.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この家に　私は一人で住んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:28.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　私には見えない何かが　ここにはいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:40.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この頃は　あまり怖くなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:47.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,多分　神様みたいなものだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:56.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここは　もう　ずっと夜だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　人形がない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また隠したのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今日も私の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:13.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの空の向こうは　どこなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここに誰もいないのは　みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:27.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの空の向こうに行ってしまったからかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:51.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんな風に　小さな空に星が輝いてるのを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:55.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,前にもどこかで見たことがある気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが綺麗で心地よくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:24.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何かを思い出すのが億劫になる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはいるか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　いねぇのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,広い家だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう時間切れか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:15.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やれやれ　今度はもう少し増やしてみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこ行ったのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,みーつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　ミズホ　何してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミと遊んでるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前まで　まだそんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,止してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,母さんはまた妙な輩を呼んでるし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いいか　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはきっと誰かに攫われちまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんが必ず探し出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もうそういうことはやめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:23.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも私　本当に見たの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それは夢だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸の底には　何にもありはしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここでしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いかがでした　イズミは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　時間切れでした
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:06.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　娘さんは確かにここで生きています
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:18.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,互いを捉えられなくなっているだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:24.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　一度に同調していられる時間は僅かです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:31.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それ以上続けると　こっちも戻ることを忘れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:35.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あちら側と水の合う者は特にね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,明日また　同調してみます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:01.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家にいるのね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:07.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　見えんかもしれんがな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:10.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さん　見えるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:20.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　いつも私の人形を誰かが持っていくの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはいつもそうしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自分の人形　持ってるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:32.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だから今も　人形を隠して　イズミと遊んでるの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また　ない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今日はどこに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,みつけたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　待て
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,話を聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前の母親に頼まれて　お前を連れ戻しにきた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:20.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は　家の裏山の古井戸に落ちて　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こっち側に来ちまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何言ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸なんて知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私の家はここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:39.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,随分と　こっちの水が合うようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:47.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　待ってる者のいるところが　お前の帰る場所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:53.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの空の向こうで　お前を待ってる者がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,毎日食事を作って待ってる母親　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人形を隠して遊んでる姉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,思い出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここは　お前のいるべき場所じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まずい　時間はねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,勝手にやらせてもらうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何して…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:47.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,戻っておいで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ね　ミズホちゃん　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸の底に星が光ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　あんなにたくさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:35.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何もないじゃない　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　もう家帰ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここで遊ぶと叱られるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　もうおいてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あー　待ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:10.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ　人形で遊ぼうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:19.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　星の数が減ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:25.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ね　私の人形貸してあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:29.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いい　すぐ返せっていうもん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　あんたにあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　見える？綺麗でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　また数が減ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ　ここにいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あったのはこれだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:59.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなはずない　私見たの　イズミが落ちるとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いい加減なことを言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ミズホ　お前またイズミと喧嘩したんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それでイズミは家を…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:15.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはどこか他の場所にきっといる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫よ　母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:35.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私　あのギンコさんの言うことを信じる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:12.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸から煙が上がったら　井戸の底に向かって呼んでください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よし　まだいるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これくらいにしとくか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これからもう一度イズミさんと同調してみます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,恐らく記憶を無くしてるはずですが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,取り戻せれば戻ってくることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:42.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,が　時間は限られている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,間に合わないようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:49.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あちら側から無理やり　こちらに繋がりを作ります
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,下準備はしてあります
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:58.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうすれば　ここからイズミさんに声が届くはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:11.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ　イズミ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:17.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ミズホちゃん　お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:33.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今の　イズミの声　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここよって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家のほうからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰だ　焚火なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:58.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:15.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,星も戻ったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:32.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　前よりだいぶ少なくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:40.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは「井星」と言ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:44.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「光脉」という生命の元の流れがぶつかる土地の井戸に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,稀に現れる現象だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:53.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　光脈がぶつかってできる火花みたいなもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:59.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつに大量に触れると　お前さんのようになっちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:07.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,数が減ってるのは　光脈の位置がずれてきてるのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:19.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何にせよ　お前には与り知れねぇ遠い世のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう別れを言うんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　もう退きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:41.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん　私　ここにはもう来ないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これ以上心配させないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:56.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん　それ　何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:20:01.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちゃんと井戸の神様が息が苦しくないようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,土の底は　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,冷たいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,苦しいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,怖いか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,寂しいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その底は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:05.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,清らかな水の　無数の星の　栖む所
